Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.08,0:00:03.43,Translation,,0,0,0,,The 20 rules are buried, the 10 commandments crushed, even public facts submerged
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:06.21,Translation,,0,0,0,,In other words: it defies prediction at every turn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.21,0:00:11.60,Translation,,0,0,0,,Yet calamity doth approach: all over, catastrophes are born screaming, trials strummed by my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:14.90,Translation,,0,0,0,,Are you still going to have that idiotic mentality?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.76,Translation,,0,0,0,,There is not a morsel for you to peck at!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:19.85,Translation,,0,0,0,,Come now, drown in endless anguish!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:27.86,Translation,,0,0,0,,Starve to death while clutching at ways to reach the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:31.01,Translation,,0,0,0,,As the moon crosses the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:34.33,Translation,,0,0,0,,the waves grow enraged
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:37.42,Translation,,0,0,0,,The cries of seagulls
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:40.77,Translation,,0,0,0,,beckon the turbulent clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.97,0:00:44.25,Translation,,0,0,0,,The golden curse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:47.25,Translation,,0,0,0,,the words left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:50.53,Translation,,0,0,0,,and the secretive smile
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:53.84,Translation,,0,0,0,,all become smeared with crimson
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:01:00.74,Translation,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for, with your eyes sealed shut?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:06.60,Translation,,0,0,0,,Try as you may to collect the shattered fragments
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:10.70,Translation,,0,0,0,,they shall spill from the hands that touch them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:13.59,Translation,,0,0,0,,and never reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:16.69,Translation,,0,0,0,,The tapestry of truth and lies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.69,0:01:22.26,Translation,,0,0,0,,Without love, it cannot be ‘seen’
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:27.00,Translation,,0,0,0,,Without love, without love, you won’t see the truth
